title: Electricity prices for households in Spain 2010 - 2018 , semi-annually
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, containing a total of 17 data points.
In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has rose over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017_S2 and 2018_S1.
Maximum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, about 23.83 was reported at Year 2018_S1
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 17.28 was reached at Year 2010_S1
